  "body": "# About\nTurn your bnundle 3D in your player's hand, while keeping the 2D sprite in the GUI. <br>\nAvailable for Java 24w11a and upwards, no mods required.\n\nDownload the **BareBones** version [here](https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/bens-bundles-bb)\n## Bundle variations\nSee what your bundle looks like in 3D!\n![All bundle colour variations](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/1f027fc41ee8d8689b10c4172d86314c1023ee87.png)\n\n<details>\n<summary>Credits</summary>\n\nModels and textures by [BennyMcCarthy](https://modrinth.com/user/BennyMcCarthy_) <br>\npack inspired by [Oreville Studio's](https://www.minecraft.net/en-us/marketplace/pdp?id=61c7a786-d7ad-49e0-a710-817121cd9795) Actions & Stuff\n\nContact: @bennymccarthy on Discord\n\n\n</details>\n\nDO NOT DISTRIBUTE\n\n\n## FAQ\n**What mods / shaders are used in the gallery images?** <br>\nThe bloom and fog effects are created in Photoshop over ordinary vanilla screenshots, and is unfortunately not a mod you can download.",
